<div class="mb-8">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">AI Post Generator</h2>
  <p class="text-base-content/60 mt-1">글 목표를 입력하면 AI가 자료를 수집·분석하여 한국어 블로그 글을 생성합니다.</p>
</div>

<div data-controller="ai-topics" class="space-y-6">
  <%# 목표 입력 폼 %>
  <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h3 class="card-title text-base">글 목표 추가</h3>

      <div class="form-control">
        <label class="label"><span class="label-text">글 목표</span></label>
        <input type="text"
               data-ai-topics-target="goalInput"
               data-action="keydown.enter->ai-topics#addTopic"
               class="input input-bordered"
               placeholder="예: SEO가 궁금한 초보 블로거를 위한 글">
      </div>

      <div class="card-actions mt-2">
        <button type="button"
                data-action="click->ai-topics#addTopic"
                class="btn btn-success btn-sm">
          + 목표 추가
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# 목표 목록 %>
  <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h3 class="card-title text-base">목표 목록</h3>

      <div data-ai-topics-target="topicsList" class="space-y-3 hidden">
        <%# 동적으로 추가됨 %>
      </div>

      <div data-ai-topics-target="emptyState" class="text-center py-6 text-base-content/40">
        아직 추가된 목표가 없습니다. 위에서 목표를 추가해주세요.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# 생성 버튼 %>
  <%= form_with url: admin_ai_writer_generate_path, method: :post, data: { "ai-topics-target": "form" } do |f| %>
    <div data-ai-topics-target="hiddenInputs"></div>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <button type="submit"
              data-ai-topics-target="generateBtn"
              disabled
              class="btn btn-primary disabled:btn-disabled">
        글 생성하기
      </button>
      <span data-ai-topics-target="topicCount" class="text-base-content/60 text-sm">
        0개의 목표
      </span>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
